<head>
    {{> head}}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-sm">
                <div class="card text-center shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row mb-2">
                            <div class="col-sm">
                                <h4 class="card-title">Iscrizioni per l'Assemblea d'Istituto del {{assemblea.info.display.date}}</h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row mb-4">
                            <div class="col-sm">
                                <span class="badge badge-primary">
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">{{student.name}} {{student.surname}} - {{student.classe}}</h5>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row mb-2" >
                            <div class="col-sm">
                                <div class="table-responsive">
                                    <table class="table table-bordered" id="labsList">
                                        <thead>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th scope="col">Ora</th>
                                                <th scope="col">Attivit√†</th>
                                                <th scope="col">Aula</th>
                                            </tr>
                                        </thead>
                                        <tbody class="text-left">
                                            {{#each student.labs}}
                                            <tr class="lab-row-confirm">
                                                <td>{{this.index}}</td>
                                                <td>{{this.labName}}</td>
                                                <td>{{this.labAula}}</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            {{/each}}
                                        </tbody>
                                    </table>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row mb-1">
                            <div class="col">
                                <small>
                                    <b class="text-small">
                                        <p>Conserva questa tabella! Ti consigliamo di salvare uno screenshot di questa schermata prima di uscire. </p><p>Potrai visualizzarla nuovamente inserendo la tua matricola nella
                                        <a href="/"> pagina di login </a></p>
                                    </b>
                                </small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer text-muted text-center text-small">
        <p class="mb-1">Copyright &copy; 2019 TronWeb | Davide Testolin | Made with Node.js</p>
    </footer>
    {{> scripts}}
</body>
